Note on source material:

The persona, place, piece, process, and position files in this folder are
original works by Kai Schlüter. They explore the experience of alcoholism,
recovery, and its absence through fictional characters and scenes.
They do not reproduce any clinical framework, therapeutic programme, or
named individual.
No intellectual property in addiction medicine, recovery literature, or
twelve-step programmes is claimed.
